---
const credentials = [
  'Scaled organic search for a leading automotive SaaS platform',
  'Technical audits across automotive, SaaS & DTC verticals',
  'Python automation for rank tracking & data pipelines',
  'Financial ROI modeling applied to SEO strategy',
  'Founder, NCR Digital — Technical SEO first, always',
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-28" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-ncr-cyan text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="inline-block h-px w-8 bg-ncr-cyan" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          About
        </p>
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-7 leading-tight">
          Architecting<br />Search Dominance.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-ncr-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            NCR Digital was built on a conviction: most agencies chase rankings. 
            We chase <span class="text-ncr-text font-medium">revenue-generating search presence</span> — 
            and we build the technical infrastructure to make it compound.
          </p>
          
          <p class="border-l-2 border-ncr-cyan/30 pl-4 italic text-sm">
            Based in Texas, <span class="text-ncr-text">NCR Digital</span> is an independent technical SEO 
            consultancy founded by <span class="text-ncr-text">Niekos Robbins</span>. We are a boutique firm 
            specializing in search engine infrastructure and are not affiliated with NCR Voyix or 
            traditional banking hardware corporations.
          </p>

          <p>
            Coming from the trenches of scaling organic search for a high-growth automotive SaaS platform, 
            the path to founding NCR Digital was clear. The gap in the market wasn't creativity — 
            it was <span class="text-ncr-text font-medium">bridging the gap between raw data and ROI</span>. 
            Most SEOs can't read a crawl log and a P&L in the same sitting. We can.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="mt-10 space-y-3" aria-label="Credentials">
          {credentials.map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-ncr-cyan font-mono mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✦</span>
              <span class="text-ncr-muted">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden lg:block relative" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="border border-ncr-border bg-ncr-card p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
          <span class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-ncr-cyan"></span>
          <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-ncr-cyan"></span>
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-ncr-cyan"></span>
          <span class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-ncr-cyan"></span>

          <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ncr-muted space-y-3 leading-loose">
            <p><span class="text-ncr-cyan">$</span> ncr analyze --domain client.saas</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-ncr-muted/70">→ crawling 12,847 pages...</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-ncr-muted/70">→ parsing Core Web Vitals...</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-ncr-muted/70">→ mapping content clusters...</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-ncr-muted/70">→ running Python rank tracker...</p>
            <div class="my-4 h-px bg-ncr-border"></div>
            <p><span class="text-ncr-green">✓</span> Opportunities identified: <span class="text-ncr-cyan">214</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-ncr-green">✓</span> Estimated traffic uplift: <span class="text-ncr-cyan">+3.2x</span></p>
            <p><span class="text-ncr-green">✓</span> Projected ROI (12mo): <span class="text-ncr-cyan">high</span></p>
            <div class="my-4 h-px bg-ncr-border"></div>
            <p class="text-ncr-muted/60"># Ready. Awaiting execution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>